snippet.title: Talisman: Digital Edition - Reaper Expansion Trailer
snippet.description:
Will you look death in the eye?
The first expansion pack for Talisman: Digital Edition, The Reaper, is available now!
The race for the Crown of Command has never been deadlier!
Link to our website - http://nomadgames.co.uk/  

Link to steam store page - http://store.steampowered.com/app/258810/ 

Talisman: Digital Edition, now available on Steam. Based on the Talisman board game, Talisman: Digital Edition recreates the 4th Revised Edition of the classic adventure board game. Choose your hero and set forth on an epic tale of dragons, treasures and magic! 

Includes online and offline multiplayer modes for up to 4 players.
